First Department,

September, 1979

(September 7, 1979) In the Matter of Thomas De Vine, Petitioner, v Bunn G. Goodman, Respondent.

Application pursuant to CPLR article 78 denied and petition dismissed, without costs and without disbursements. Concur—Murphy, P. J., Birns, Bloom, Markewich and Silverman, JJ.
